Datenbetrieb Basic Machine Definitions (packer)
====================================================

install packer (download from packer.io)


${PACKER_DIR}/packer validate ${TEMPLATE}.json

${PACKER_DIR}/packer build ${TEMPLATE}.json


vagrant box remove ${BOXNAME} virtualbox
vagrant box add ${BOXNAME} $(BOXFILE}.box

Veewee (obsolete)
====================================================

https://github.com/datenbetrieb/veewee

veewee gem must be installed from source (>=0.3.8.dev)


- export PROVIDER=vbox
- veewee $PROVIDER build
- veewee $PROVIDER export
- mv XX.box boxes/.
- scp boxes/XX.box h01n:/srv/www/boxes.datenbetrieb.de/.
